name: The Desert Traveller 2
description: Travel isn’t always pretty. It isn’t always comfortable. Sometimes it hurts, it even breaks your heart. But that’s okay. The journey changes you; it should change you. It leaves marks on your memory, on your consciousness, on your heart, and on your body. You take something with you. Hopefully, you leave something good behind” – Anthony Bourdain AI Created Photoshop enhanced JPG file 960 x 1240 pixels Twitter @ Bans_ji
